name: GameOn365
body:
Welcome to GameOn365 on GitHub.

We publish:
* Bukkit/Spigot plugins
* BungeeCord plugins
* Garry's Mod gamemodes
* PHP classes for communication between a website and game servers
* Other gaming-related bits of code we create

Links:
* [GameOn365 Forums - Talk to us!](http://gameon365.net)
* [Warcraft365 on GitHub - World of Warcraft addons and projects](http://github.com/warcraft365)
* [Stormjive Interactive on GitHub - General (non-gaming) projects](http://github.com/stormjive)
